useReducer hook-
________


useReducer is a hook that is used for state management

It is an alternative for useState

useState is build using useReducer

____-


useReducer is a primitive hook

_________

useReducer is related to reducer

________




console.log(Array.reduce(reducerfuncton, intialvalue))



Const Recucerfunction = (acc, currentVal) => acc + currentVal


